<h2>Está bem! Intensivkurs Portugiesisch (Sonstiges)</h2>
<h3></h3>
<hr>
<abbr class='unapi-id' title='1854'></abbr>
<div class='row-fluid'>
<div class='span8'>
<h3>Allgemeine Angaben</h3>
